These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite  | tea |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
City: edinburgh, prague
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| City   | edinburgh | prague |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, folk
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Music-Genre       | folk  | r&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different games are played: chess, bridge
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Game   | chess  | bridge |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
